A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Public Health – Home Health Care Providers – Directory
3 FOR the purpose of requiring the Maryland Department of Health to establish and
4 maintain an online directory of each home health care provider; requiring that the
5 directory allow an individual to search the directory and identify a home health care
6 provider based on specified criteria; and generally relating to home health care
7 providers.
